<xsd:schema targetNamespace="urn:common.exchange.schema.fisheries.ec.europa.eu:v1" xmlns:common="urn:common.exchange.schema.fisheries.ec.europa.eu:v1" xmlns:exchange="urn:exchange.schema.fisheries.ec.europa.eu:v1" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/wsdl/soap/" xmlns="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/wsdl/"> <xsd:import namespace="urn:movement.exchange.schema.fisheries.ec.europa.eu:v1" schemaLocation="Movement.xsd"/> <xsd:import namespace="urn:types.plugin.exchange.schema.fisheries.ec.europa.eu:v1" schemaLocation="Plugin.xsd"/> <xsd:import namespace="urn:exchange.schema.fisheries.ec.europa.eu:v1" schemaLocation="Exchange.xsd"/> <xsd:element name="exchangeFault"> <xsd:complexType> <xsd:sequence> <xsd:element name="code" type="xsd:int"/> <xsd:element name="message" type="xsd:string"/> </xsd:sequence> </xsd:complexType> </xsd:element> <xsd:complexType name="keyValueType"> <xsd:sequence> <xsd:element name="key" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:element name="value" type="xsd:string"/> </xsd:sequence> </xsd:complexType> <xsd:simpleType name="AcknowledgeTypeType"> <xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"> <xsd:enumeration value="OK"/> <xsd:enumeration value="NOK"/> </xsd:restriction> </xsd:simpleType> <xsd:complexType name="AcknowledgeType"> <xsd:sequence> <xsd:element name="messageId" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:element name="message" type="xsd:string" minOccurs="0"/> <xsd:element name="type" type="common:AcknowledgeTypeType"/> <xsd:element name="pollStatus" type="common:PollStatusAcknowledgeType" minOccurs="0" maxOccurs="1"/> <xsd:element name="unsentMessageGuid" type="xsd:string"/> </xsd:sequence> </xsd:complexType> <xsd:complexType name="PollStatusAcknowledgeType"> <xsd:sequence> <xsd:element name="status" type="exchange:ExchangeLogStatusTypeType"/> <xsd:element name="pollId" type="xsd:string"/> </xsd:sequence> </xsd:complexType> <xsd:complexType name="CommandType"> <xsd:sequence> <xsd:element name="pluginName" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:element name="command" type="common:CommandTypeType"/> <xsd:element name="timestamp" type="xsd:dateTime" minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1"/> <xsd:choice> <xsd:element name="poll" type="plugin:PollType"/> <xsd:element name="email" type="plugin:EmailType"/> </xsd:choice> <xsd:element name="unsentMessageGuid" type="xsd:string" minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1"/> <xsd:element name="fwdRule" type="xsd:string"/> </xsd:sequence> </xsd:complexType> <xsd:simpleType name="CommandTypeType"> <xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"> <xsd:enumeration value="POLL"/> <xsd:enumeration value="EMAIL"/> </xsd:restriction> </xsd:simpleType> <xsd:complexType name="ReportType"> <xsd:sequence> <xsd:element name="type" type="common:ReportTypeType"/> <!--<xsd:element name="version" type="xsd:string"/>--> <xsd:element name="recipient" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:element name="recipientInfo" type="movement:RecipientInfoType" minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="unbounded"/> <xsd:element name="timestamp" type="xsd:dateTime" minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1"/> <xsd:choice> <xsd:element name="movement" type="movement:MovementType"/> <!--<xsd:element name="elog" type="xsd:string"/>--> </xsd:choice> <xsd:element name="unsentMessageGuid" type="xsd:string" minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1"/> </xsd:sequence> </xsd:complexType> <xsd:simpleType name="ReportTypeType"> <xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"> <xsd:enumeration value="MOVEMENT"/> <!--<xsd:enumeration value="ELOG"/>--> </xsd:restriction> </xsd:simpleType> </xsd:schema>

minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="1"/> </xsd:sequence> </xsd:complexType> <!--Type received in UNIONVMS--> <xsd:complexType name="MovementBaseType"> <xsd:sequence> <xsd:element name="assetId" type="asset:AssetId"/> <xsd:element name="mobileTerminalId" type="mobterm:MobileTerminalId"/> <xsd:element name="comChannelType" type="movement:MovementComChannelType"/> <xsd:element name="source" type="movement:MovementSourceType"/> <xsd:element name="position" type="movement:MovementPoint"/> <xsd:element name="positionTime" type="xsd:dateTime"/> <xsd:element name="status" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:element name="reportedSpeed" type="xsd:double" nillable="true"/> <xsd:element name="reportedCourse" type="xsd:double" nillable="true"/> <xsd:element name="movementType" type="movement:MovementTypeType"/> <xsd:element name="activity" type="movement:MovementActivityType"/> <xsd:element name="assetName" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:element name="flagState" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:element name="externalMarking" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:element name="ircs" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:element name="mmsi" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:element name="tripNumber" type="xsd:double" nillable="true"/> <xsd:element name="internalReferenceNumber" type="xsd:string"/> </xsd:sequence> </xsd:complexType> <xsd:complexType name="MovementPoint"> <xsd:sequence> <xsd:element name="longitude" type="xsd:double" nillable="true"/> <xsd:element name="latitude" type="xsd:double" nillable="true"/> <xsd:element name="altitude" type="xsd:double" nillable="true"/> </xsd:sequence> </xsd:complexType> <!--Plugin type--> <xsd:simpleType name="MovementComChannelType"> <xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"> <xsd:enumeration value="FLUX"/> <xsd:enumeration value="MANUAL"/> <xsd:enumeration value="NAF"/> <xsd:enumeration value="MOBILE_TERMINAL"/> </xsd:restriction> </xsd:simpleType> <xsd:simpleType name="MovementTypeType"> <xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"> <xsd:enumeration value="POS"/> <xsd:enumeration value="ENT"/> <xsd:enumeration value="EXI"/> <xsd:enumeration value="MAN"/> </xsd:restriction> </xsd:simpleType> <!--LES (eg. InmarsatC EIK), ev. free text field--> <xsd:simpleType name="MovementSourceType"> <xsd:restriction base="xsd:string"> <xsd:enumeration value="INMARSAT_C"/> <xsd:enumeration value="IRIDIUM"/> <xsd:enumeration value="CAN"/> <xsd:enumeration value="NOT"/> <xsd:enumeration value="AUT"/> <xsd:enumeration value="SUS"/> <xsd:enumeration value="COB"/> <xsd:enumeration value="CAT"/> <xsd:enumeration value="RET"/> <xsd:enumeration value="OBR"/> <xsd:enumeration value="ANC"/> <xsd:enumeration value="DRI"/> <xsd:enumeration value="FIS"/> <xsd:enumeration value="HAU"/> <xsd:enumeration value="PRO"/> <xsd:enumeration value="STE"/> <xsd:enumeration value="TRX"/> <xsd:enumeration value="OTH"/> </xsd:restriction> </xsd:simpleType> <!--type sent to FLUX--> <xsd:complexType name="MovementType"> <xsd:complexContent> <xsd:extension base="movement:MovementBaseType"> <xsd:sequence> <xsd:element name="guid" type="xsd:string"/> <!--unionvms specific--> <xsd:element name="connectId" type="xsd:string"/> <!--unionvms specific--> <xsd:element name="calculatedCourse" type="xsd:double" nillable="true"/> <xsd:element name="measuredSpeed" type="xsd:double" nillable="true"/> <xsd:element name="calculatedSpeed" type="xsd:double" nillable="true"/> <xsd:element name="segmentIds" type="xsd:string" minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="2"/> <xsd:element name="metaData" <xsd:sequence> <xsd:element name="closestPort" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:element name="distanceToClosestPort" type="xsd:double" nillable="true"/> <xsd:element name="closestCountryCoast" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:element name="distanceToCountryCoast" type="xsd:double" nillable="true"/> <xsd:element name="areas" type="xsd:string" minOccurs="1" maxOccurs="unbounded"/> </xsd:sequence> </xsd:complexType> <xsd:complexType name="MovementActivityType"> <xsd:sequence> <xsd:element name="messageType" type="movement:MovementActivityTypeType"/> <xsd:element name="messageId" type="xsd:string"/> <xsd:element name="callback" type="xsd:string"/> </xsd:sequence> </xsd:complexType> </xsd:schema>
